biz.onomato.frskydash.domain

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.onomato.frskydash.domain.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    A Model as it is configured by the user. A Model should be of a certain type (car, airplane, helicopter, quad, ...) and have a certain name so the user can recognize it. For the frsky telemetry part a Model also has a collection of Channel objects that are listening for incoming values. And a collection of Alarm configurations that can be set to the FrSky Module.
    Author:
    Espen Solbu
